songs.title: ZOOM
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus: Travis Scott]
Gotta stay down, ya ain't got no zoom
Big rock, diamonds, Yao Ming yoom (Yeah)
Purple lemonade, puffin' out them fumes
Heatin' up like last day in June (Ha)

[Verse: Gunna & Travis Scott]
Niggas stealin' my drip, that shit ain't cool
See Gunna gettin' tags, let me floss my jewels
I cherish her face, I pay for her groom (Yeah)
No time, no way so I'm takin' off soon
Cash out on drip, tryna fly to the moon'
Lookin' like "who is he?"
Gunna no runner, he move like me, yeah
Got foreigns, a moving fleet
To Travis like "Who is security?"
I fly her right in then meet up at the room
She don't know your name but she know all my tunes
I pass it to Los, and he shot it to Junes
You can't try none the brothers, the brothers try you (Yeah)
If you try one of us you get put on the news (Yeah)
Pull up in that new Bentley truck
Bag full of money and all of these hunnids is blue
I know you proud of me, A.P., I don't do apologies
I’m high too on my Prada tee, purchase on my new AMIRI jeans
Young Gunna drip god, I fly with no wings
I let her use my card to secure her needs (Yeah)
Had to tell her girl these pearls, not beads (Yeah)
Gettin' high in the sky without my weed
